# Environment variable template for CmdTab.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` (which is gitignored) and fill in real values locally.
# Never commit `.env` or any real secret values.
#
# No environment variables are referenced by the code yet. Add them here as the
# project grows, one per line, with a short comment describing each:
#
# EXAMPLE_API_KEY=        # what it is used for
